        "timestamp": "2020-06-25 00:04:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> is  'etcd-m3db-operators' also an 'app' in the composite app or is it somehow different?  Just curious why it is not under 'app4'.\n\nActually, operators are prerequisites for m3db, but they don't directly form the part of the stack, so thought they should not come under the family of sub-apps denoted by app1, app2, app3, all of which independently exist and form the core of the stack.",
